    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They kept up the-- the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a beautiful garden, which still stays in my memory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The garden-- they kept at that time-- you know, which was very seldom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a gardener, a special gardener.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was kept some trees, which I didn't see-- they used to call it overseas trees, which I discover they have them here in Australia, but I never saw them in Poland, and the roses, and-- and-- and it was really beautiful.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
